meals.name: Chicken Biscuit

meals.name: Chick-n-Minis 4ct
meals.description: Bite-sized Chick-fil-A® Nuggets nestled in warm, mini yeast rolls that are lightly brushed with a honey butter spread.

meals.name: Egg White Grill
meals.description: A breakfast portion of grilled chicken with a hint of citrus, served on a toasted multigrain English muffin with egg whites and American cheese.

meals.name: Greek Yogurt Parfait w/ Granola
meals.description: Creamy, organic vanilla bean Greek yogurt with fresh berries and your choice of toppings.

meals.name: Bacon, Egg & Cheese Biscuit

meals.name: Chicken, Egg & Cheese Bagel

meals.name: Hash Brown Scramble Bowl w/ Nuggets
meals.description: A hearty morning meal of sliced Chick-fil-A Nuggets, crispy Hash Browns, scrambled eggs and a blend of Monterey Jack and Cheddar cheeses. Made fresh each morning. Served in a convenient bowl. Served with Jalapeño Salsa.

meals.name: Spicy Southwest Salad w/ Grilled Filet (Cold)
meals.description: Slices of grilled spicy chicken breast served on a fresh bed of mixed greens, topped with grape tomatoes, a blend of Monterey Jack and Cheddar cheeses, and a zesty combination of poblano chiles, red bell peppers, roasted corn and black beans. Made fresh daily. Served with Seasoned Tortilla Strips, Chili Lime Pepitas, Creamy Salsa dressing or 2 packets of Jalapeño Salsa for an option with fewer calories (or guest’s choice of dressing).

meals.name: Spicy Southwest Salad w/ No Chicken
meals.description: Slices of grilled spicy chicken breast served on a fresh bed of mixed greens, topped with grape tomatoes, a blend of Monterey Jack and Cheddar cheeses, and a zesty combination of poblano chiles, red bell peppers, roasted corn and black beans. Made fresh daily. Served with Seasoned Tortilla Strips, Chili Lime Pepitas, Creamy Salsa dressing or 2 packets of Jalapeño Salsa for an option with fewer calories (or guest’s choice of dressing).

meals.name: Cobb Salad w/ Nuggets
meals.description: Chick-fil-A® Nuggets, freshly breaded and pressure-cooked, sliced and served on a fresh bed of mixed greens, topped with roasted corn kernels, a blend of shredded Monterey Jack and Cheddar cheeses, crumbled bacon, sliced hard-boiled egg and grape tomatoes. Made fresh daily. Served with Charred Tomato and Crispy Red Bell Peppers. Pairs well with Avocado Lime Ranch dressing.

meals.name: Cobb Salad w/ No Chicken
meals.description: Chick-fil-A® Nuggets, freshly breaded and pressure-cooked, sliced and served on a fresh bed of mixed greens, topped with roasted corn kernels, a blend of shredded Monterey Jack and Cheddar cheeses, crumbled bacon, sliced hard-boiled egg and grape tomatoes. Made fresh daily. Served with Charred Tomato and Crispy Red Bell Peppers. Pairs well with Avocado Lime Ranch dressing.

meals.name: Market Salad w/ Grilled Filet (Cold)
meals.description: Sliced grilled chicken breast served on a fresh bed of mixed greens, topped with crumbled blue cheese and a mix of red and green apples, strawberries and blueberries. Made fresh daily. Served with Harvest Nut Granola, Roasted Almonds and Light Balsamic Vinaigrette dressing (or guest’s choice of dressing).

meals.name: Grilled Nuggets 8ct
meals.description: Bite-sized pieces of freshly marinated boneless breast of chicken, grilled for a tender and juicy backyard-smoky taste. Available with guest's choice of dipping sauce.

meals.name: Grilled Cool Wrap
meals.description: Sliced grilled chicken breast nestled in a fresh mix of Green Leaf lettuce with a blend of shredded Monterey Jack and Cheddar cheeses, tightly rolled in a flaxseed flour flat bread. Made fresh daily. Pairs well with Avocado Lime Ranch dressing (or guest’s choice of dressing).

meals.name: Chick-fil-A Nuggets 8ct
meals.description: Bite-sized pieces of boneless chicken breast, seasoned to perfection, freshly-breaded and pressure cooked in 100% refined peanut oil. Available with choice of dipping sauce.

meals.name: Grilled Chicken Sandwich
meals.description: A lemon-herb marinated boneless breast of chicken, grilled for a tender and juicy backyard-smoky taste, served on a toasted Multigrain bun with Green Leaf letttuce and tomato. Pairs well with Honey Roasted BBQ sauce.

meals.name: Chick-fil-A Chicken Sandwich
meals.description: A boneless breast of chicken seasoned to perfection, hand-breaded, pressure cooked in 100% refined peanut oil and served on a toasted, buttered bun with dill pickle chips. Gluten-free bun or multigrain bun also available at an additional cost.

meals.name: Chick-fil-A Deluxe Sandwich w/ American Cheese
meals.description: A boneless breast of chicken seasoned to perfection, hand-breaded, pressure cooked in 100% refined peanut oil and served on a toasted, buttered bun with dill pickle chips, Green Leaf lettuce, tomato and American cheese. Gluten-free bun or multigrain bun also available at an additional cost.

meals.name: Chicken Quesadilla
meals.description: The Chicken Quesadilla is a purist’s meal; and we say 'purist' in the most complimenting way possible. It’s a simple flour tortilla with some grilled chicken, a hefty portion of melted three-cheese blend, creamy jalapeño sauce, and absolutely zero bells and whistles.

meals.name: Cheese Quesadilla
meals.description: The Cheese Quesadilla may appear to be basic but it is all things great. In fact, the Cheese Quesadilla often gets offended when it is referred to as being basic. Do you blame it?

meals.name: Power Menu Bowl
meals.description: The Power Menu Bowl is a real-life version of a video game power-up. Your choice of grilled chicken or steak, guacamole, reduced fat sour cream, freshly prepared pico de gallo, seasoned black beans, crisp romaine lettuce, and seasoned rice, packed into a seriously powerful bowl.

meals.name: Power Menu Bowl - Veggie
meals.description: Hear us out. It’s all the same fixings as the the Power Menu Bowl with the guacamole, reduced fat sour cream, freshly prepared pico de gallo, crisp romaine lettuce, and seasoned rice, packed into a seriously powerful bowl. But substitute the meat for a double portion of seasoned black beans.
